<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8">
		<meta name="viewport" content="maximum-scale=1.0,minimum-scale=1.0,user-scalable=0,width=device-width,initial-scale=1.0"/>
		<meta name="format-detection" content="telephone=no,email=no,date=no,address=no">
		<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="../../zui/css/mzui.css">
		<title>title</title>
		<style>
			body {
				background-image: url('../../icon/b2.jpg');
				background-repeat: no-repeat;
				-webkit-background-size: cover;
				-moz-background-size: cover;
				-o-background-size: cover;
				background-size: cover;
				background-color: #915906;
			}
			.word {
				text-align: center;
				color: #A7ADA3;
				font-size: 20px;
				font-weight: bold;
				bottom: 1%;
				position: fixed;
				height: 30%;
				padding: 3px;
			}
			.main {
				height: 100%;
				width: auto;
			}
			.edit {
				margin: 1rem;
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<div class="pull-right circle info btn edit" onclick="op()">
			<i class="icon icon-key"></i>
		</div>
		<div class="word">
			<blockquote>
				现实中生活中我们遇到的有关亲情、爱情、家庭、梦想、未来等各式各样的烦恼,别人也许已经经历过,说不定就会有个陌生人可以解答你的疑惑
				——解忧杂货店
			</blockquote>
		</div>
	</body>
	<script type="text/javascript" src="../../script/api.js"></script>
	<script type="text/javascript">
		var dialogBox = null;
		apiready = function() {
			dialogBox = api.require('dialogBox');
		};
		function op() {
			dialogBox.scene({
				rect : {
					w : 280,
					h : 400
				},
				texts : {
					title : '情景1',
					content : '火车售票处前的队伍蜿蜒纵横，旁边一小伙一边张望，一边将手伸向前面买票人的口袋，啊，是小偷!',
					okBtnTitle : '确定'
				},
				styles : {
					bg : '#fff',
					title : {
						bg : '#aaa',
						h : 44,
						size : 14,
						color : '#000'
					},
					content : {
						color : '#111',
						size : 12
					},
					ok : {
						bg : '#89a',
						titleColor : '#f00'
					}
				}
			}, function(ret, err) {
				if (ret) {
					alert(JSON.stringify(ret));
				} else {
					alert(JSON.stringify(err));
				}
			});
		}
	</script>
</html>